---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Pocket Door Hinge Repair & Replacement | Expert Service in Florida"
  description="Squeaking, sagging, or misaligned pocket door hinges? Expert hinge repair and replacement in Orlando, Miami & Fort Myers. We diagnose the root cause. Call (954) 727-5410."
>

  <!-- Hero -->
  <section class="relative bg-primary text-white py-6 md:py-8 overflow-hidden">
    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-cover bg-center opacity-20" style="background-image: url('/images/services/hinge-repair.webp')" role="img" aria-label="Pocket door hinge repair and replacement service"></div>
    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-r from-primary/75 to-primary/50"></div>
    <div class="relative max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4">
      <div class="max-w-2xl">
        <h1 class="font-heading text-5xl md:text-7xl tracking-wide mb-4">Pocket Door Hinge Repair & Replacement</h1>
        <p class="text-xl md:text-2xl font-light mb-4 text-gray-200">Stop the Squeak, Fix the Sag, Restore the Swing</p>
        <p class="text-base md:text-lg text-gray-300 mb-8">
          A squeaking hinge is annoying. A sagging hinge causes the door to bind, scrape the frame, and wear unevenly — creating bigger problems down the line. We don't just oil the hinge and call it done. We find out why it's failing and fix the actual cause.
        </p>
        <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 mb-12">
          <a href="tel:9547275410" class="bg-white text-primary font-heading text-xl tracking-wide px-8 py-4 rounded hover:bg-gray-100 transition-colors text-center" aria-label="Call Pocket Door Services">
            (954) 727-5410
          </a>
          <a href="/contact" class="border-2 border-white text-white font-heading text-xl tracking-wide px-8 py-4 rounded hover:bg-white hover:text-primary transition-colors text-center">
            FREE ESTIMATE
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Main Content -->
  <section class="py-16 bg-white">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center">
      <div>
        <h2 class="font-heading text-4xl md:text-5xl tracking-wide text-primary mb-4">The Real Problem Is Rarely the Hinge Itself</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed mb-6">
          When a pocket door hinge starts squeaking or sagging, the instinct is to replace it. But in most cases, the hinge is a symptom — not the cause. Stripped screw holes, a warped frame, settling walls, or a door that's too heavy for its hinge rating are the real culprits. Replace the hinge without addressing those, and you'll be replacing it again in six months. Our <a href='/blog/pocket-door-lock-hinge-problems-guide' class='text-accent hover:underline'>pocket door lock and hinge problems guide</a> breaks down when repair makes sense vs when full replacement is the better investment.
        </p>
        <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed mb-6">
          Our technicians inspect the full hinge system: the hinge itself, the screw anchoring, the frame condition, the door weight, and the alignment. If the screw holes are stripped, we repair the wood and re-anchor with proper fasteners. If the door is too heavy for the installed hinges, we upgrade to hardware rated for the load. If the frame has shifted, we shim and realign.
        </p>
        <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
          We work with all hinge types — butt hinges, concealed hinges, heavy-duty commercial hinges, and pivot hinges. For pocket doors specifically, we also check that hinge-related issues aren't masking a deeper problem with the <a href='/service/roller-replacement-and-frame-repair' class='text-accent hover:underline'>roller or track system</a>.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div>
        <img src="/images/pocket door 2.webp" alt="Pocket door hinge repair and replacement in Florida" class="rounded-lg shadow-lg w-full" loading="lazy" />
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Why Choose Us -->
  <section class="py-16 bg-gray-light">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4">
      <h2 class="font-heading text-4xl md:text-5xl text-center tracking-wide text-primary mb-10">Why Choose Pocket Door Services</h2>
      <div class="grid grid-cols-2 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-6">
        {[
          { name: "Fast & Reliable", icon: "M13 10V3L4 14h7v7l9-11h-7z" },
          { name: "Transparent Pricing", icon: "M12 8c-1.657 0-3 .895-3 2s1.343 2 3 2 3 .895 3 2-1.343 2-3 2m0-8c1.11 0 2.08.402 2.599 1M12 8V7m0 1v8m0 0v1m0-1c-1.11 0-2.08-.402-2.599-1M21 12a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z" },
          { name: "Emergency 24/7", icon: "M12 8v4l3 3m6-3a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z" },
          { name: "Expert Technicians", icon: "M16 7a4 4 0 11-8 0 4 4 0 018 0zM12 14a7 7 0 00-7 7h14a7 7 0 00-7-7z" },
        ].map((f) => (
          <div class="text-center p-6 bg-white rounded-lg shadow-sm">
            <div class="w-14 h-14 bg-accent rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-3">
              <svg class="w-7 h-7 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d={f.icon} /></svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="font-heading text-lg tracking-wide text-primary">{f.name}</h3>
          </div>
        ))}
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Other Services -->
  <section class="py-16 bg-white">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4">
      <h2 class="font-heading text-4xl md:text-5xl text-center tracking-wide text-primary mb-10">Our Other Services</h2>
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
        {[
          { name: "Roller Replacement & Frame Repair", href: "/service/roller-replacement-and-frame-repair", image: "/images/old tracks.webp" },
          { name: "Lock Repair", href: "/service/lock-repair", image: "/images/new lock.webp" },
          { name: "Commercial Door Installation", href: "/service/commercial-door-installation", image: "/images/client photo.webp" },
          { name: "Commercial Door Repair", href: "/service/commercial-door-repair", image: "/images/walk through.webp" },
          { name: "Commercial Door Lock Services", href: "/service/commercial-door-lock-services", image: "/images/worker.webp" },
        ].map((s) => (
          <a href={s.href} class="group bg-white rounded-lg overflow-hidden shadow-md hover:shadow-xl hover:-translate-y-1 transition-all duration-300 border border-gray-border/30">
            <div class="aspect-[4/3] overflow-hidden">
              <img src={s.image} alt={`${s.name} service`} class="w-full h-full object-cover group-hover:scale-105 transition-transform duration-300" loading="lazy" />
            </div>
            <div class="p-5">
              <h3 class="font-heading text-2xl tracking-wide text-primary">{s.name}</h3>
            </div>
          </a>
        ))}
        <div class="flex flex-col justify-center items-center bg-primary rounded-lg shadow-md p-8 text-center text-white">
          <svg class="w-10 h-10 mb-4 text-accent" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M3 5a2 2 0 012-2h3.28a1 1 0 01.948.684l1.498 4.493a1 1 0 01-.502 1.21l-2.257 1.13a11.042 11.042 0 005.516 5.516l1.13-2.257a1 1 0 011.21-.502l4.493 1.498a1 1 0 01.684.949V19a2 2 0 01-2 2h-1C9.716 21 3 14.284 3 6V5z" /></svg>
          <h3 class="font-heading text-2xl tracking-wide mb-2">Not Sure What You Need?</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-300 text-sm mb-4">Tell us what's going on with your door and we'll recommend the right service. Free estimates, no obligation.</p>
          <a href="/contact" class="inline-flex bg-accent text-white font-heading tracking-wide px-6 py-3 rounded hover:bg-blue-600 transition-colors">GET A FREE ESTIMATE</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- From Our Blog -->
  <section class="py-16 bg-gray-light">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 text-center">
      <h2 class="font-heading text-3xl tracking-wide text-primary mb-4">From Our Blog</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-600 mb-6">Learn more about pocket door hinge issues and when to repair vs replace.</p>
      <a href="/blog/pocket-door-lock-hinge-problems-guide" class="group inline-flex items-center gap-3 bg-white rounded-lg shadow-md p-6 hover:shadow-xl transition-all border border-gray-border/30 text-left">
        <img src="/images/new lock.webp" alt="Pocket door lock and hinge repair" class="w-24 h-24 rounded-lg object-cover flex-shrink-0" />
        <div>
          <h3 class="font-heading text-xl tracking-wide text-primary group-hover:text-accent transition-colors">Pocket Door Lock & Hinge Problems: Repair vs Replace</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-500 text-sm mt-1">March 10, 2026 · 9 min read</p>
        </div>
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA -->
  <section class="py-16 bg-primary text-white text-center">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4">
      <h2 class="font-heading text-4xl md:text-5xl tracking-wide mb-4">Hinges Squeaking, Sagging, or Broken?</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-300 leading-relaxed mb-8">
        Let us diagnose the root cause — not just the symptom. Our pocket door hinge specialists serve Orlando, Miami, and Fort Myers with same-day diagnostics and reliable repairs.
      </p>
      <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center">
        <a href="tel:9547275410" class="inline-flex bg-accent text-white font-heading text-xl tracking-wide px-8 py-4 rounded hover:bg-blue-700 transition-colors">Call Now (954) 727-5410</a>
        <a href="/contact" class="inline-flex border-2 border-white text-white font-heading text-xl tracking-wide px-8 py-4 rounded hover:bg-white hover:text-primary transition-colors">FREE ESTIMATE</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

</Layout>
